title: Green Bean Casserole
directions: MIX soup, milk and pepper in a 1 1/2 -qt. baking dish. Stir in beans and 2/3 cup French Fried Onions.
BAKE at 350°F for 30 min. or until hot. Stir.
TOP with remaining 2/3 cup onions. Bake 5 min. until onions are golden.
ingredients: 1 can (10 3/4 oz.) Campbell's® Condensed Cream of Mushroom Soup
1 1/3 cups FRENCH'S® Original or Cheddar French Fried Onions
